14
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,200
Mr.Jian Mo.

15
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:54,640
Going to bed this early?

16
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:56,640
That's a real 'grandpa'schedule.

17
