95
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,440
I'm working hard too!

96
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,400
If I hadn't kept the boss company while drinking,

97
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,280
how else would he agree

98
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,880
