99
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,720
Actually, there are some things

100
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,760
You don't need to worry about so much.

101
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:52,600
Don't worry?

102
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:55,560
Don't worry?

103
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,159
They're going to eat me alive!

104
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,240
Mr.Jian Mo.

105
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,680
We heard you and Xu Xinglang don't get along.

106
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,360
Is that true?

107
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,040
Word is you look down on his acting.

108
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,480
Are you just jealous of his looks?

109
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:17,960
Then this time

110
