188
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,040
Get closer.

189
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,680
What are you doing with your hand?

190
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,320
I’m striking a pose!

191
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,320
What's wrong with you

192
