204
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,800
And Jian Mo...

205
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:20,480
He’s radiating tension and rejection.

206
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,160
This just isn't working.

207
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,840
wait

208
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,200
That’s a wrap for today.

209
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,080
You two can go back and rest.

210
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,600
