228
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:12,480
Right?

229
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:14,680
Right.

230
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,000
Where are you going, Jian Mo?

231
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,680
I...

232
