233
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:36,840
I’m just...

234
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,160
Just...

235
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,240
Just...

236
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:40,240
Stop.

237
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,120
That "I'm just"

238
