247
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,240
The second "just"...

248
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,160
is

249
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,160
hesitation.

250
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,320
The third "just"...

251
00:10:59,320 --> 00:10:59,800
is

252
