254
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,200
I’m not running away.

255
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,880
I’m just...

256
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,720
Just...

257
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,200
Just...

258
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,200
Hear the difference?

259
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,400
Not at all.

260
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,280
Forget it.

261
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,760
I guess I can't coach you then.

262
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:24,880
