267
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:39,120
Xinglang has a few scenes,

268
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,360
Could you help him fine-tune his performance?

269
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,160
Xinglang,

270
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:44,880
I’m going out to grab some food.

271
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:47,040
Be a good student and learn from Mr.Jian Mo, okay?

272
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:47,960
Bye!

273
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,040
Teacher Jian Mo,

274
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,760
