275
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:55,720
Xu Xinglang,

276
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:57,960
We need to talk.

277
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,680
First of all,

278
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,920
I have no issue with your lifestyle.

279
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,720
And I have no intention of interfering.

280
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,120
Ionly ask

281
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,120
